d['c'] = 3     # add new key
del d['b']     # remove key
d.keys()       # dict_keys(['a','c'])
d.values()     # dict_values([1,3])
d.items()      # dict_items([('a',1),('c',3)])
5. Comprehensions
List Comprehension
